bio: I am a computer science student looking for good food.

A tech enthusiast by day, and a culinary adventurer by night. From coding to cooking, I blend my passion for software technology with my insatiable appetite for trying new flavors. As a student, I've embarked on a mouthwatering mission to visit and review every restaurant in town.

Fisher Pratt, a student at De La Salle University Manila, is an adventurous food enthusiast on a mission to uncover the best culinary delights along Taft Avenue. With a passion for exploring diverse flavors, Fisher navigates the bustling streets, from cozy eateries to trendy cafes, in search of hidden gastronomic gems. His culinary journey is fueled by a love for food and a desire to share his discoveries with others.

I'm Antonio Agapito, a student at the University of Santo Tomas. I'm a dedicated food enthusiast on a never-ending quest for unforgettable culinary experiences. Exploring every nook and cranny of Manila, I seek out hidden gems and indulge in the vibrant flavors that make our city so special. Join me as I embark on a delicious journey through the world of food.

Hi!, I'm Cindy, a devoted student at Arellano University, embarking on a journey to pursue a degree in political studies. However, my passion for food is what truly ignites my spirit. I have an insatiable appetite for culinary adventures, constantly exploring diverse cuisines and seeking out hidden food gems. Balancing my academic pursuits with my love for food, I embody the essence of a curious, well-rounded student with a taste for both knowledge and delectable flavors.
